Package test.runs

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Run
    Describes one command that is to be run on the interactive console as well as its expected output.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorRun
    A test run for an error message.
    ExactRun
    A test run for exact matching.
    LineRun
    A test run for matching the method's whole output for one command line by line.
    NoOutputRun
    A test run that may not output anything at all.
